# 🩸 Community Blood

A continuous donor–patient matching network—not just another one-time blood drive.

Community Blood is a full-stack blood donation management system that connects verified blood donors with patients in need. Instead of relying solely on scheduled blood drives, the platform enables donors to register once and receive notifications when their blood type is required nearby.

---

## 🚀 Features

### 👤 Donor
- Register with personal and blood donation details
- OTP-based email verification
- Log blood donations
- View donation history
- Track donation status (Pending, Approved, Rejected)
- Update profile information

### 🛠️ Admin
- Secure admin authentication
- Verify donor accounts
- Approve or reject donation requests
- Manage donor records
- View government ID for verification
- Monitor blood inventory
- Manage upcoming blood drives

### 🌐 Public
- View live blood inventory
- Check blood availability status
- Browse upcoming blood donation drives
- Learn how the platform works
- Contact administrators

