## 📡 REST API

The frontend communicates with the Laravel backend through RESTful APIs using Axios.

Example API endpoints:

```
POST   /api/register
POST   /api/login
POST   /api/logout
GET    /api/profile
POST   /api/donations
GET    /api/donations
GET    /api/inventory
```

