## ⚙️ Installation

### Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/community-blood.git
```

### Frontend

```bash
cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev
```

### Backend

```bash
cd backend
composer install
cp .env.example .env
php artisan key:generate
php artisan migrate
php artisan serve
```

